<HEADLINE>
FT  17 DEC 92 / Stock &amp; Currency Markets
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
 -----------------------------------------------------
STOCK MARKET INDICES
 -----------------------------------------------------
FT-SE 100: 2,732.8 (+14.9)
Yield 4.48
